com.cerner.bunsen.definitions

Class HapiContainedConverter<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.cerner.bunsen.definitions.HapiConverter<T>
      • com.cerner.bunsen.definitions.HapiContainedConverter<T>
  • Type Parameters:
    T - the type of the schema produced by the converter.

    public abstract class HapiContainedConverter<T>
extends HapiConverter<T>
    Partial converter implementation for contained structures. Contained converters are distinct from HapiCompositeConverter in that a Contained converter must translate between a static Resource Container and FHIR's Any-typed container list of FHIR resources.
